item.title: CVE-2023-49681|2023-12-21T23:06:19.930Z -- kashipara%20group -- job%20portal
item.description: Job Portal v1.0 is vulnerable to multiple Unauthenticated SQL Injection vulnerabilities. The 'cmbQual' parameter of the Employer/InsertWalkin.php resource does not validate the characters received and they are sent unfiltered to the database.
